OL,3,CAurigny defends airfares as Guernsey
OL,4,Chas different 'requirements'
OL,6,FAn Aurigny spokesperson says: "It is
OL,7,Fworth noting that subsidies play a
OL,8,Frole in other markets that enable
OL,9,Flower airfares on selected routes, but
OL,10,Fthis was not factored into the
OL,11,Fcomparative analysis.
OL,13,F"The report does find that fares
OL,14,Foffered by Aurigny are lower on more
OL,15,Fcomparable regional routes, such as
OL,16,FExeter, where such subsidies do not
OL,17,Fplay a central role.
