OL,3,CAurigny defends airfares as Guernsey
OL,4,Chas different 'requirements'
OL,6,F"As a smaller market, with a greater
OL,7,Fpropensity to travel, Guernsey also
OL,8,Fhas differing scalability
OL,9,Fopportunities and schedule
OL,10,Frequirements compared to other Crown
OL,11,FDependencies.
OL,13,F"Everyone at Aurigny remains committed
OL,14,Fto serving the needs of Guernsey's
OL,15,Fcommunity, contributing to the
OL,16,Fisland's economic and social
OL,17,Fwellbeing, and delivering the best
OL,18,Fpossible value for money."
