OL,3,CAurigny defends airfares as Guernsey
OL,4,Chas different 'requirements'
OL,6,FSports clubs like Guernsey Raiders RFC
OL,7,Fregularly fly to games off-island and
OL,8,Fsay they spend around #100,000 on
OL,9,Fairfares each year.
OL,11,FChris Gnapp from the club explains:
OL,12,F"Flights are getting incredibly
OL,13,Fexpensive and even the smallest raise
OL,14,Fin prices has a really heavy impact on
OL,15,Fthe club due to the number of flights
OL,16,Fwe're taking.
OL,18,FThe States of Guernsey says higher
OL,19,Ffares are due to the high demand for
OL,20,Ftravel in Guernsey and the size of
OL,21,Faircraft flying to and from the island.
