OL,3,CAurigny defends airfares as Guernsey
OL,4,Chas different 'requirements'
OL,6,FAndrew Eggleston from Alderney's
OL,7,FChamber of Commerce tells ITV News
OL,8,Fthat many islanders feel Alderney is
OL,9,Fbeing unfairly targeted.
OL,11,FHe explains: "It seems to be all based
OL,12,Fagainst Alderney, that's how it comes
OL,13,Fover.
OL,15,F"Have prices increased on all the
OL,16,Fother regional fares and such that
OL,17,FAurigny already has? Not that we've
OL,18,Fheard of, at all."
